<a name="toc_tc27988"></a><p>&nbsp;</p><div> <table class="tc" width="90%" ><tr><th colspan="4">Test Case P237-1: TC01_ECP_Valid_Adaugare_Produs&nbsp;<span style="font-size: 80%;">[Version  : 1]</span></th></tr>
